我一直想掩饰病情这样我就能去了
And I've been trying to hide it so I could go,

362
00:16:23,590 --> 00:16:25,390
但我不想害他生病
but I don't want to make him sick.

363
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:27,290
是啊
Yeah.

364
00:16:27,290 --> 00:16:30,490
的确  你看上去既苍白又汗涔涔的
Yeah, you do look pretty pale and clammy.

365
00:16:34,560 --> 00:16:36,360
是啊
Yeah.

366
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:39,200
玩得开心点
Have fun.

367
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:41,370
好吧  好好休息  好吗
Well, feel better, okay?

368
00:16:48,180 --> 00:16:51,150
我平时不就是苍白且汗涔涔的嘛
No, that's just my regular pale and clammy.

369
00:16:53,380 --> 00:16:56,820
我是说  真的  更危险的不是质量损失
I mean, really, the bigger danger isn't the loss of mass.

370
00:16:56,820 --> 00:16:57,950
而是它会耗尽用于
Instead, it will run out of hydrogen

371
00:16:57,950 --> 00:16:59,790
核燃料的氢气
to use for nuclear fuel,

372
00:16:59,790 --> 00:17:03,290
膨胀成为红巨星  然后把地球烤焦
swell up into a red giant, and fry the Earth.

373
00:17:03,290 --> 00:17:06,660
所以你不想分吃一份沙拉是吗
So you don't want to split a salad?

374
00:17:06,660 --> 00:17:07,660
不了  谢谢
No, thank you.

375
00:17:07,660 --> 00:17:09,000
但说到分东西
But speaking of splitting things,

376
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:11,130
你听说过可以提高光合效率的
did you hear about the light-splitting greenhouse film

377
00:17:11,130 --> 00:17:13,770
分光温室膜吗
that could improve photosynthetic efficiency?

378
00:17:13,770 --> 00:17:15,500
没有
No.

379
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:17,540
只是我在照顾我制造的一个小人时
Just a little something I read

380
00:17:17,540 --> 00:17:19,810
读到的一点东西
while nursing a human being that I made.

381
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:23,140
我就点个鸡肉好了
I'm just gonna get the chicken.

382
00:17:24,150 --> 00:17:26,580
日哦肉  机一鸡  倒念鸡肉
N-E-K-C-I-H-C: chicken backwards.

383
00:17:26,580 --> 00:17:29,380
见识妈妈大脑的厉害
Boom, mom brain.

384
00:17:30,850 --> 00:17:33,050
还喝了一整瓶酒
And a whole bottle of wine.

385
00:17:37,090 --> 00:17:38,690
认输了吧
In your face!

386
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:48,340
嗨
Hello?

387
00:17:48,340 --> 00:17:50,910
嗨  亲爱的  你感觉怎么样
Aw, hey, sweetie, how you feeling?

388
00:17:50,910 --> 00:17:53,040
还好  我在休息
Okay. I'm just resting.

389
00:17:53,040 --> 00:17:55,980
我有个惊喜也许能让你感觉好点
Well, I have a surprise that might make you feel better.

390
00:17:55,980 --> 00:17:56,880
是吗
Oh, really?

391
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:59,010
是啊  看看这是谁
Yeah, look who's here.

392
00:18:02,490 --> 00:18:04,720
等等  我记得你
Wait, I know you.

393
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:08,360
不  你不记得
No, you don't.

394
00:18:08,360 --> 00:18:09,890
不  我记得
Yes, I do.

395
00:18:09,890 --> 00:18:12,560
你在我的酒店等我
You were waiting for me at my hotel.

396
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:15,030
你毁了我的领带
You ruined my tie.

397
00:18:15,030 --> 00:18:16,430
等等  什么
Wait, what?

398
00:18:16,430 --> 00:18:17,670
他在说什么
What's he talking about?

399
00:18:17,670 --> 00:18:21,740
他  很显然  他在开玩笑
Uh, he, uh-- obviously, he's kidding.

400
00:18:21,740 --> 00:18:23,240
很好笑  比尔
That's a, that's a good one, Bill.

401
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:25,410
我得挂了
I got to go.

402
00:18:27,610 --> 00:18:30,240
笨蛋莱纳德
Stupid Leonard,

403
00:18:30,250 --> 00:18:33,450
去见笨蛋比尔・盖茨
meeting stupid Bill Gates,

404
00:18:33,450 --> 00:18:37,580
不带我这个笨蛋
without stupid me.

405
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:49,230
我很抱歉  谢尔顿
I am so sorry-- Sheldon?

406
00:18:49,230 --> 00:18:52,400
莱纳德  我没法生你的气
Oh, Leonard, I can't stay mad at you.

407
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:54,300
来吧
Come here.

408
00:18:54,300 --> 00:18:56,470
我接受你的道歉了
Apology accepted.

409
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:59,140
晚餐吃什么  我饿坏了
What's for dinner? I'm starving.

410
00:19:05,650 --> 00:19:07,480
你好
Hola.

411
00:19:17,510 --> 00:19:18,880
你们两位女士还好吗
How are you ladies doing?

412
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:21,180
如果感到开心你就举举手
Raise your hands if you're bueno.

